Installation

    git clone https://github.com/jlisinski/dotvim.git ~/.vim


Create symbolic links

    ln -s dotfiles/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s dotfiles/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc


Get plugins as git submodules

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Configure Pathogen 

    mkdir ~/.vim/autoload
    ln -s ~/.vim/pathogen/pathogen.vim ~/.vim/autoload/pathogen.vim
 



